      </h2>
      <div
        style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;"
      >
        <div class="info-card-base step-card">
          <div class="icon-box" style="background: #e0f2fe;">üìû</div><h4>1. Immediate Contact</h4><p>Call our {cityName} dispatch line.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card-base step-card">
          <div class="icon-box" style="background: #fef3c7;">üìã</div><h4>2. Professional Quote</h4><p>An arborist reviews your trees near {landmark}.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card-base step-card">
          <div class="icon-box" style="background: #dcfce7;">‚úÖ</div><h4>3. Project Done</h4><p>Licensed work with full site cleanup.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ARBORIST LOCAL DATA REPORT (KORUNDU) -->
    <section style="margin-top: 4rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;">
        <div class="info-card-base" style="border-top: 4px solid #ea580c;">
