                <div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 12px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
                    <strong style="display: block; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase;">Neighborhood Character</strong>
